Happy NewYear ! It was the most magical day when I was little. Beautiful shiny ornaments on the tree, windows covered in icy patterns and that magical feeling you only feel when you are little. So, no magical feelings anymore😅 but other things are present. And the  presents. 

Year was so weird. Ambivalent year, Ambivalent emotions. Terrible war Russian government started is in one corner. And giving birth to my  Beautiful daughter is in the other. 

I wish peace in the New Year. And I wish safety to all the children out there. And I want to believe in magic again. 
Happy New Year !

My morning #skincareroutine is here for you:
1) @versed Daily Brightening solution toner with 4 acids (and gosh, i love AHAs )
2) @clarinsusa Double serums for the face amd for the eyes. Really helps with my dry skin of breastfeeding mom
3) @humanrace humidifying cream mixed with fee drops of @dermalogica phyto replenish oil. This oil doesn't brake out my skin, or clogges the pores. It smells very nice as well. 
4) @welovecoco face massaging tool that works the same way as #guashatools
Let me know if you have any questions or want me to tell you about something specific! I'm here to share my knowledge 😘😏

Just a reminder how real people look without filters and makeup 🤣🤣🤣🤣 we have pores, breakouts, blood vessels, pigmentation,  wrinkles, and grey hair. A lot of grey hair 😅😅😅 and yet we have happy eyes and adventurous hearts despite the fact we have all kinds of problems. Keep calm and carry on!

And here is what that face (check the previous post) can look with some makeup on 😅😄😆
I love makeup. I don't think we should #makeup to deny who we are. You are unique, and makeup is just the way to play. I think of it as an accessory or your face. What's your mood today? What's your look? It's not that serious 😅🤣😂

One of the finest moments of my career was designing #makeuplooks for this  incredible show #24decadesofpopularmusic by @taylormacnyc 
This is when I gave an eternity long French kiss. Because all my beauty campaigns, all my editorials and fashion stories will be forgotten soon enough. And this one will be remembered. Because it has an incredible purpose. It has meaning. And it is true art, when makeup becomes a part of something really wonderful. Something very important. If you don't know what this show is about, you have a chance to see a documentary on @streamonmax created by Oscar winning directors @jeffreyfriedman and @epsteinrob 
Produced by @pomegranatearts with @machinedazzle @mattraymusic and the whole wonderful #24decades family!!!

Well, it's the vacation mode! I'm getting ready for productive fall and winter 💪
And since we're here, I'd like to remind you not to use a chemical sunscreen when you're on vacation! It's bad for you and it's bad for the environment. Go with mineral formula and organic beauty brands! I personally LOVE tinted #sunscreen from @rmsbeauty 
And another traveler beauty staple is my #skincarekit from @sixgldn it has everything I need, quality is great and the size is perfect!

Let the #halloween begin! Me as the lord of light few years ago. You don't have to look scary to celebrate Halloween.
#beautifulhalloween #makeupideas #halloweencostume #halloweenlook
So here we go!!!!! #halloweenlook #beautifulhalloween

And some video of my #halloweenlook :) I don't like to look scary for Halloween. Every year I create a fantasy look all by myself. Concept, costume makeup... All done by me :))) The toxic jellyfish has UV lights installed in the headpiece so she always glows!!! Let me know what you think:)

Last night makeup took literally 7 min :)))) The main face design feature is the appliques I created for this look. I used sequins and rhinestones to decorate and shapes were made with my face measurements. I had an online class how to make those and was wondering if I want to do another class! Let me know in comments if you'd take it!
